{"tid":384511,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"［七月十四］一人一件懷疑自己撞鬼經歷","createTime":"2017-09-02T11:03:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-02T11:26:52.000Z","uid":128845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8ffa249488b845b43cb3ca606096729fdb2e97d3","tid":384511,"uid":128845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T11:03:49.000Z","msg":"夜晚點幾兩點打緊機，突然收到個電話，見到老母打俾我，老母打黎唔得人驚啊，得人驚既係我老母一早收咗工翻咗黎屋企訓著咗，我即刻走去阿媽間房，點知佢熟睡緊，我開佢部手機見佢冇打俾我，但我手機仲響緊&hellip;我屌&hellip;即刻關機。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4c1743bd99966709551274f73ca960b7b871a5b","tid":384511,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T11:13:35.000Z","msg":"其實訓緊嗰個唔係你老母.....<br />\n<br />\n真個個打電話俾你求救"},{"pid":"912a05f75d22a754408293a425917910008fecec","tid":384511,"uid":94835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T11:15:59.000Z","msg":"訓緊個嗰&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17194a362c2ce6ca87cad1e959261b21bccd4c04","tid":384511,"uid":128845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T11:26:52.000Z","msg":"每次老母打黎個心都離一離<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}